Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.32,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:29.78,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:47.80,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:20.55,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.39,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:36.19,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:29.78,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:47.80,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:20.55,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.39,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:36.19,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:48.28,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,270)}Ep. 45 - Tob Disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:43.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There. Come out, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really wish you'd lay way more eggs than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sticky, Pansy, Soppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I got up way too early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:47.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems even Little,\Nthe usual early bird, is not awake yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I got up awfully early,\Nsince I haven't slept at home for such a long while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not particularly early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, it was me who overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:08.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like mom and the others are still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with everyone? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Because you've been missing\Nfor three days straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,everyone lost their sleep to the worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:23.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So we turned into a sleepless family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We were {\i1}that{\i0} much worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:31.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you, but but could you please\Nmilk the goat this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No "Buts!" I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:37.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you bring these to the kitchen for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is mom really still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I overslept so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been losing sleep\Nfor these three nights too, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:01.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thinking about Lucy,\NI couldn't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I gotta go wake Clara up before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Clara is still asleep too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:07.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:11.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then do go wake her up\Nand then hurry up to milk the goats, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is on that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my? She is up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Lucy's the only one who hasn't been losing sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:22.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, she led a somewhat queen-like life\Nin Mr. Princeton's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:29.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I return home,\NI'm made to do some chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn is later!\NBetter go wake Clara up if you've nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it! What are you doing?\NBe a good girl and wait for your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But say, everyone has sure been\Nworried about me a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:07.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We were all deprived of sleep\Nby worries about Lucy who wouldn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But upon seeing Lucy return safely,\Nthe whole family felt a great relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And so, every single one of us overslept that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Wait just a moment, it's almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really hungry. I am hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I also gotta leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you could still probably fit in some time for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have that luxury.\NI wanted to catch the first stagecoach of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also overslept dreadfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Lucy's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the garden, tending to goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, I'm returning to the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And you won't be back until next Saturday again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you give everyone so much worry anymore, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have nice week!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished with mine already, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you hurry up to bring it to mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? It's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning to the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:41.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd better quit the customs job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The salaries there aren't anything spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I stumble upon any other place that pays better,\NI think should rather transfer to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like your current job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. This is a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the salary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, I'll start working again.\NOnce I do, we'll have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you concern, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. We'll work it out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already found a good job, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Though I still haven't decided on it for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I found it.
Comment: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:22.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You hear me, right?\NMr. Popple's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna go to the meadows\Nfor the first time in a while, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... Oh, right.\NIt's Mr. Princeton's carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Lucy. Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be shy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:21.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My wife insisted on me bringing it along. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unload the rest of the luggage, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will do, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:36.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How did it feel last night\Nto finally return to your own home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:38.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I slept like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true what they say - no place like home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means your husband\Nis currently looking for a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:58.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But he said he had come up\Nwith some promising plan when he left today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'd not have this problem if you had the land, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:09.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true. But the way things stand now,\Nour every attempt to get a plot came to naught... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:15.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um. If that wouldn't trouble you too much,\Nplease give my best regards to your missus too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:19.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really feel like I'll never be able to repay\Neverything you've done for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you have some free time,\Nplease be sure to visit us at our place at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:31.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As I stated last night, I'm interested in discussing some agricultural matters with your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:34.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. I'll pass it to my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:36.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll have my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:41.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you'd like us to keep\Nsuch a wonderful doll and dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't feel right, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please do! There are no children in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've no need for a doll or for a girl's dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You even wore such a lovely dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:59.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And walked in these shoes!\NMy, you really {\i1}was{\i0} living like a queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the gift, of course,\Nbut they don't really fit with this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is it bad to have a queen in our house too? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Being a queen and all... Is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's a pretty dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:21.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to knock before entering a lady's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:21.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:26.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, our guest is leaving already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:33.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't help like something was very off this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:36.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,as if our own daughter\Nhad suddenly disappeared yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:42.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My wife. I mean, Sylvia,\Nseems particularly saddened by this fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She absolutely wants you to come play around more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your siblings are welcome to tag along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, we are so grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy! He said I can come visit them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, when are we going, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:23.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, that gentleman wants\Nto discuss something thoroughly with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, bring dad along when you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go too, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I can really go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:04.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Well, I figured I should let everyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I was waiting until everyone gets together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Ben is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:15.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, I've met with the mining company man\Nto inquire into their job opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "mine?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Like, coal digging job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, the iron ore digging job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a dangerous job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a little dangerous,\Nbut the wage is accordingly high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd rather you not do such a dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain degree of risk to any job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:46.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, couldn't you apply for job at some big farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be the one most fitting job for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:55.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've had my share of working thanklessly\Nat another's farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd go to work on a farm,\Nit won't be another's farm, but my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, why mine, of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:06.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Actually, what I wanted\Nto talk to everyone about is this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:14.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, if I want to work at a mine,\NI'd also have to live close to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean we'll have to move too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The company offers cheap housing for its workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:22.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll sell this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:27.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, if we put aside as much money as we can,\Nin five years, we'll have enough to buy our own plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:31.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're going to work at a mine\Nso as to buy the plot in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's near Mount Barker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Barker?\NThat's a long way from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:42.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want everyone to be ready for a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to work at Mrs. Mac's store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:55.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Probably?" Commuting to here\Nfrom Mount Barker would be totally impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll have to quit, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try asking John for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:04.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:08.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you two planning to get married soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:19.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also by no means opposed\Nto Clara and John getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You two could stay to live in Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that fine by you, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:26.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He can keep working\Nat the customs office as he does now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:36.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be awfully difficult for him to go home all the way to the Mount Barker every Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to me like everyone is getting scattered\Nall over the place, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:45.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no certainty to any of this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow or the day after that,\Nwe'll hire a cart and go check out the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I would definitely like you all to see the place\Nthat I myself have not yet been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup! Giddyup! Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:09.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We went to see the mine\Nwhere dad was going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:15.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Coincidentally, we went there to look at the company lodgings that we'll soon be occupying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The scenery is becoming so deserted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That there is the Mount Barker, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They won't have a school\Nat a place like that. Right, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:53.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are working on the mine, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe about 80 workers or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled!\NThere won't be any school in a place like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can never know that for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I actually wanted to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad for you, but you won't be getting any school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it!\NI'd rather not move here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm all for it!
Comment: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:22.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you said "mine," I thought more of a big hole,\Nwhich you enter to dig out coal and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All the mines in this area are open-pit type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there are many ores\Nthat are close to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This seems way less dangerous\Nthan descending into a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:32.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where would be the place that we'll live in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look. See an arrangement of houses over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But those are pretty small houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They only seem small when you look at them from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:50.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. Even if we get closer,\Nthey won't get much bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:56.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I need to meet someone in the office.\NAre you coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We probably don't have to come, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:01.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You could get off here\Nand I'd pick you up on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:02.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:04.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kangaroos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why would there be kangaroos\Nwhere the grass is so sparse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:14.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, "sparse" doesn't mean there's none at all.\NLook, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! There are kangaroos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On the second thought, those are probably\Nnot kangaroos, but wallabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're a little smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't they just be babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:33.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're not! Look, look.\NThey even have actual babies in their pouches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:33.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go catch a kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wallaby, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:51.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to stay around here, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also need to check out the company lodgings anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:19:59.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful around the cliffs over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:02.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go now, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:08.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! You're the oldest one, so look after everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not like that, Tob!\NThey'll run away if you rush so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But those kangaroos aren't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Those are wallabies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try getting a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:27.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:41.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you haven't signed the official contract yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:53.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wanted to see the actual place first,\Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if so, feel free to look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:00.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,May I also go look at the company lodgings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:03.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, without a doubt.\NI'll show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:06.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. I take it you don't have any kids, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We do. We'll bring along three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:21.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you using gunpowder too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. That's just someone hunting kangaroos, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kangaroos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They've a delicious mean\Nand a hide that can be used in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:32.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And there just happens to be a lot of them around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:55.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you shooting them! Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:58.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're so evil, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:04.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he managed to shoot any wallabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see any fall on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:11.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I really wonder\Nwhy'd they wanna kill such cute animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:19.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:22.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really catch something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch it I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, okay, Tob?
Comment: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:51.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet hit the parent wallaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:54.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what'll happen to the baby now?
