Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:09.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:16.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's cute, we probably won't be able\Nto raise it from such little age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:17.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:20.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already! Come back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:30.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:35.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Answer me! Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:40.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
