Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:43.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:47.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob! Come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Where are you?
